<textHTML>&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;Divide the class into two groups&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Ask students to pick a partner from the opposite group and present to them what he/she ate for breakfast this morning&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Ask privately Group 1 to present in the most bummed out way and Group 2 to present in the most excited way&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;</textHTML>
