<column>ICI</column>
<textHTML>&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;Explain what the activity asked each group to do&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Explain how conveying moods is an important part of giving a good presentation; if people are bored, it means the presenter may be conveying a bored mood&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Encourage students to practice picking a mood and conveying it in their presentations (e.g. inspiring, moving, funny, call to arms, etc.)&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;</textHTML>
